Package server.model

Class Item

  • java.lang.Object
    • server.model.Item
  • public class Item
extends java.lang.Object
    Provides data fields and methods for tools that the store carries. Stores ID-number, tool name, the quantity in stock, the tool's price, and a Supplier object for the supplier of the tool.
    Since:
    February 4, 2019
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    M. Moshirpour, Nick Park, Carter Shaul
